penner-up
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:also called sheep-o in sheep-shearing, one who keeps the shearers' pens supplied with sheep
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:compare fleece-o
Pronunciation:
